reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars This does not properly fit a 30z Stanley.
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this bag explicitly because it stated in the title that was geared to fit both the 30oz and the 40oz Stanleys, and I was struggling to find one that listed compatibility for my 30oz.Unfortunately, it doesn't fit - the bottom won't go all the way in so it's got like an air pocket and it won't stand up properly. Additionally, the part that is supposed to go around the handle doesn't fit right because the height between the 30oz & 40oz are not the same so it basically doesn't properly close the velcro underneath.The quality of the actual product is good, and I can imagine it would work great with a 40oz Stanley as that is what it's clearly built for.
